== 商业模型 ==
安利将单层次直销与多层次直銷两种方式相结合。安麗的经销商被称为“直銷商”（ABO,Amway Business Owner），他们不但与潜在的顾客面对面交流、销售，也会将感兴趣的人引進成為直銷商行列。[[哈佛商学院|哈佛商学院]]认为安利是“世界上最赚钱的直销公司之一”，其创办者温安洛和狄维士“通过金字塔式的多层次直销，让安利的直銷商不但能从自己的销售额中拿到一定比例的獎金，还能拿到他们发展下线的销售额比例裡的另外獎金”。<ref name="HarvardBS">{{cite news |title=American Business Leaders of the Twentieth Century – Richard M. DeVos, Amway Corporation |url=http://www.hbs.edu/leadership/database/leaders/richard_m_devos.html |accessdate=2011-05-17 |newspaper=[[哈佛商学院|哈佛商学院]] |year=2011 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308220607/http://www.hbs.edu/leadership/database/leaders/richard_m_devos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 产品 ==
安利旗下的产品涵盖了清洁剂、美容、保健、滤水器、功能饮料等方面。2017年，安利报告称其总销售额为86亿美元，其中按地区由高到低排序依次是中国大陆、美国、韩国、日本、泰国、台湾、印度、俄罗斯、马来西亚和香港。<ref name="dsn2018">{{cite web |author1=DSN Staff |title=Amway Reports 2017 Sales Slightly Down at $8.6 Billion {{!}} Direct Selling News |url=https://www.directsellingnews.com/amway-reports-2017-sales-slightly-down-at-8-6-billion/ |website=Direct Selling News |publisher=直销新闻 |accessdate=2018-06-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180622210329/https://www.directsellingnews.com/amway-reports-2017-sales-slightly-down-at-8-6-billion/ |archivedate=2018-06-22 |language=en-us |date=2018-02-13 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>

安利的生产线从最初创立时买下的液态有机清洁剂开始发展，后引入了洗衣粉 SA8 （1960年）、化妆品系列{{tsl|en|Artistry (cosmetics)|雅姿}}（1968年）。目前，安利生产的产品超过450种，其工厂分布于中国、印度和美国，纽崔莱有机农场分布于巴西、墨西哥和美国。安利旗下的品牌有雅姿、逸新（Atmosphere）、Body Blends、Bodykey、Body Works、Clear Now、益之源（eSpring）、Glister、iCook、Legacy of Clean、纽崔莱、Perfect Empowered Drinking Water、Personal Accents、Ribbon、丝婷（Satinique）、Artistry Men和{{tsl|en|XS Energy Drink|XS功能饮料|XS}}。

=== 纽崔莱 ===
{{Main|纽崔莱}}
纽崔莱（{{lang|en|Nutrilite}}，在某些国家是{{lang|en|Nutriway}}）健康系列产品是安利最大的品牌，2008年纽崔莱全球销量超过30亿美元。<ref>{{cite web |author=e-point SA |url=http://www.amway.ua/cms/visitor_news_new/Newsroom?news_id=10819 |title=Nutrilite passes $3 billion mark in annual sales |publisher=Amway.ua |accessdate=2011-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903233610/http://www.amway.ua/cms/visitor_news_new/Newsroom?news_id=10819 |archivedate=2011-09-03 }}</ref>2017年，纽崔莱依然是安利旗下的主导产品之一，和2016年相比销售额仍在大幅增长。<ref name="dsn2018" />

2001年，五款纽崔莱产品成为首批获得[[美國國家衛生基金會|美國國家衛生基金會]]认证的节食产品。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nsf.org/business/newsroom/soe01-3/dietary.html |title=NSF International Announces Dietary Supplements Certification Program |publisher=Replay.web.archive.org |date=2008-12-14 |accessdate=2011-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081214123716/http://www.nsf.org/business/newsroom/soe01-3/dietary.html |archivedate=2008-12-14 }}</ref>2006年至2009年间，纽崔莱赢得了马来西亚、中国大陆、台湾、泰国和全亚洲《Reader's Digest》“亚洲信赖品牌”的白金奖、金奖。<ref name="f">{{cite web |url=http://www.rdasiatrustedbrands.com/ |title=Reader's Digest Trusted Brands Asia |publisher=Rdasiatrustedbrands.com |accessdate=2011-07-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715160237/http://www.rdasiatrustedbrands.com/ |archivedate=2011-07-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>2008年，因其对营养和基因互动上的研究，纽崔莱的研发人员与安达高的子分支{{lang|en|Interleukin Genetics}}赢得了第十二届约翰·M·肯尼营养与代谢奖（{{lang|en|John M. Kinney Award for Nutrition and Metabolism}}）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nutritionjrnl.com/webfiles/images/journals/nut/jmk_winners_2008.pdf |title=Nutrition |format=PDF |accessdate=2011-07-09 |archive-date=2013-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130414093339/http://www.nutritionjrnl.com/webfiles/images/journals/nut/jmk_winners_2008.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2011年，纽崔莱品牌的维他命、膳食补充剂在安利的销售额排到了第一，总共有47亿美元。<ref name="grbj-20120227">{{cite news|last1=Daly|first1=Pete|title=Amway grew in almost all regions in 2011|url=http://www.grbj.com/articles/73925|accessdate=2016-03-25|publisher={{tsl|en|Grand Rapids Business Journal||Grand Rapids Business Journal}}|date=2012-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404193530/http://www.grbj.com/articles/73925|archive-date=2016-04-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>据 Euromonitor International 报告，2014年纽崔莱在维他命和膳食补充剂方面的销量均为世界第一。<ref name="euromonitor-amway-claims">{{cite web|title=Amway Claims|url=http://www.euromonitor.com/amway-claims|website=www.euromonitor.com|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112010419/https://www.euromonitor.com/amway-claims|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年，Euromonitor International报告安利是中国第一大维他命和膳食补充剂供应商，占市场11%，年销售额达1000亿人民币（折合156亿美元）。<ref name="twsj-20150818">{{cite news|last1=Loretta|first1=Chao|title=Amway's Made in America Strategy Scores with Asian Customers|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/amways-made-in-america-strategy-scores-with-asian-customers-1439912608|accessdate=2016-03-25|publisher=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|date=2015-08-18|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309205129/https://www.wsj.com/articles/amways-made-in-america-strategy-scores-with-asian-customers-1439912608|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，同年，根据中国顾客秘密品牌调查，安利纽崔莱是中国最受欢迎的维他命与膳食补充剂品牌。<ref name="ft-20150514">{{cite news|last1=Plowright|first1=Matthew|title=China's vitamin market harder to crack for western companies|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/f1c82b58-fa2c-11e4-b432-00144feab7de.html#axzz42wLkveBF|accessdate=2016-03-25|publisher=[[金融時報|金融時報]]|date=2015-05-14|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808035042/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/f1c82b58-fa2c-11e4-b432-00144feab7de.html#axzz42wLkveBF|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年1月，安利宣布自愿[[產品召回|召回]]一批纽崔莱和XS功能饮料。{{tsl|en|Peanut Corporation of America|美国花生公司}}为这些产品提供了原料，当中可能含有被[[沙門氏菌屬|沙門氏菌屬]]污染的成分。安利称并没有收到任何与产品相关的病例报告。<ref name=Nutriliterecall1>{{cite web| title = Amway Global Announces Nationwide Recall Of XS® Energy Bar Chocolate Nut Roll And Expansion Of Nutrilite® Energy Bars Recall Because Of Possible Health Risk| publisher = [[美国食品药品监督管理局|美国食品药品监督管理局]]| date = 2009-02-04| url = http://www.fda.gov/Safety/Recalls/ArchiveRecalls/2009/ucm128349.htm| accessdate = 2011-05-13| archive-date = 2017-05-07| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170507194802/https://www.fda.gov/Safety/Recalls/ArchiveRecalls/2009/ucm128349.htm| dead-url = no}}</ref>

2012年，{{tsl|en|Center for Science in the Public Interest|公共利益科学中心|美国公共利益科学中心}}（CSPI）控诉安利称其在Nutrilite Fruits & Vegetables 2GO Twist Tubes的产品描述中使用了未经证实且不合法的语句，并称如果安利不对此采取补救措施的话，那么他们要为此提起集体诉讼。<ref name="CSPI_022812">{{cite web|title=Amway Makes Illegal Deceptive Claims for its Nutrilite Twist Tubes|url=http://www.cspinet.org/new/201202281.html|publisher={{tsl|en|Center for Science in the Public Interest||Center for Science in the Public Interest}}|accessdate=2016-03-25|date=2012-02-28|archive-date=2016-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616095129/http://www.cspinet.org/new/201202281.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="UPI_022812">{{cite news|title=Group alleges Amway deception|url=http://www.upi.com/Health_News/2012/02/28/Group-alleges-Amway-deception/73941330487788/|accessdate=2016-03-25|publisher=[[合众国际社|United Press International]]|date=2012-02-28|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225063405/https://www.upi.com/Health_News/2012/02/28/Group-alleges-Amway-deception/73941330487788/|dead-url=no}}</ref>安利回应称，那些对产品的描述用语都已经获得核实，他们也不打算更改产品标语，但仍然会针对CSPI的顾虑展开审核。<ref>{{cite web|title=CSPI Threatens Amway with Lawsuit|url=http://www.nutraceuticalsworld.com/contents/view_online-exclusives/2012-04-05/cspi-threatens-amway-with-lawsuit|date=2012-04-05|access-date=2018-06-22|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226001035/https://www.nutraceuticalsworld.com/contents/view_online-exclusives/2012-04-05/cspi-threatens-amway-with-lawsuit|dead-url=no}}</ref>CSPI后报告，安利同意在2014年年末更改产品标签。<ref>{{cite web|title=Litigation Project – Current Docket|url=https://www.cspinet.org/litigation/current.html|publisher=Center for Science in the Public Interest|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621085543/http://www.cspinet.org/litigation/current.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

